text: Læa meux thut khxng rea (ma la xik ah) di ma ha lut khea pen thukkh pheraa phwk khea læa klaw thi ca hı khwam khumkhrxng mi di dangnan (ma la xik ah) cung klaw wa xya klaw læa sera sok seiycı thæcring rea pen phu chwyhelux than læa briwar khxng than wentæ phriya khxng than pheraa nang xyu nı hmu phu thuk thalay
